{"tid":1643521,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"終於畀佢等到！莫天才勢回歸英超","createTime":"2019-10-10T07:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T06:56:42.000Z","uid":246731,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d20398e920cf57eb523b6470b80ecfa391bcde","tid":1643521,"uid":246731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:14:04.000Z","msg":"前曼聯領隊、有「莫天才」之稱嘅莫耶斯，好大機會回歸英超，再次執掌愛華頓！今夏愛華頓使咗超過1億鎊買人，諗住喺聯賽大展拳腳，但勢估唔到依家排緊尾3，領隊馬高施華好大機會落鑊。莫耶斯曾經帶領愛華頓11年，成功到畀費格遜賞識引荐到曼聯，據英媒報道佢極希望再教「拖肥糖」。<br />\n<br />\n愛華頓本季演出令人非常失望，開季2勝1和5負，依家身處降班區域，馬高施華相信好快被炒。莫耶斯02年至13年帶領愛華頓踢出極具效率嘅實務足球，相信唔少拖肥迷都好掛住佢。莫耶斯於18年夏天被韋斯咸炒魷後一直未有工開，依家以3.25倍成為愛華頓下任領隊大熱，好大機會「愛回家」。"},{"pid":"9d0bf273985a24f45fef1b30d8d74a801bca0c38","tid":1643521,"uid":60695,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:30:17.000Z","msg":"12/1到12/21愛華頓㗎快車又幾癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n12/1 李斯特城<br />\n12/5 利物浦<br />\n12/7 車路士<br />\n12/14 曼聯<br />\n12/21 阿仙奴"},{"pid":"b56b448ef963306aaac3fb910364217acdb082de","tid":1643521,"uid":246731,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"獌就算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係利，車，阿最難搞"},{"pid":"8bab47969a5e440c50949f798dbc320b488abd93","tid":1643521,"uid":251052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"回家吧"},{"pid":"816433bc5a64b6105e23893bbf3bd80a4f51bad0","tid":1643521,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"@2&amp;b<br />\n點睇"},{"pid":"2568fc246df20cdac8214622d5e99331d8110c02","tid":1643521,"uid":151324,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d0bf273985a24f45fef1b30d8d74a801bca0c38","tid":1643521,"uid":60695,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-1